OL,3,C'One in 10 young carers have missed
OL,4,Cschool exam due to looking after loved
OL,5,Cones'
OL,7,FOne in 10 young carers have missed a
OL,8,Ftest or exam because of their caring
OL,9,Fresponsibilities, according to new
OL,10,Fpolling.
OL,12,FThe findings have prompted a charity
OL,13,Fto call for a specialist staff member
OL,14,Fin every school, college and
OL,15,Funiversity to proactively look out for
OL,16,Fyoung carers and ensure they get the
OL,17,Fright support.
