OL,7,FThe Carers Trust's survey, carried out
OL,8,Fby Opinium, also found that half of
OL,9,Fyoung carers spend less than an hour
OL,10,Feach day seeing friends and taking
OL,11,Fpart in hobbies or other activities,
OL,12,Fthanks to their role in looking after
OL,13,Fa loved one.
