OL,7,FOf the 350 young carers aged eight to
OL,8,F17 from across the UK, who look after
OL,9,Fa family member or relative with an
OL,10,Fillness, disability, addiction or poor
OL,11,Fmental health, 57% said they spend
OL,12,Fless than an hour each day doing their
OL,13,Fhomework and 44% said they spend
OL,14,Fbetween three and four hours a day on
OL,15,Ftheir caring role.
