OL,7,FThe charity said the move would not
OL,8,Fnecessarily require a new staff member
OL,9,Fto be brought in, but rather that an
OL,10,Fexisting worker could be given
OL,11,Fresponsibility specifically for young
OL,12,Fcarers.
OL,14,FMs McHugh said: "Every aspect of your
OL,15,Flife can be affected, from how you do
OL,16,Fin school to whether you can see your
OL,17,Ffriends. This can affect children as
OL,18,Fyoung as five and the impact extends
OL,19,Fall the way into adulthood.
