OL,3,C'One in 10 young carers have missed
OL,4,Cschool exam due to looking after loved
OL,5,Cones'
OL,7,F"It's high time the Government ensured
OL,8,Fevery school and college had a young
OL,9,Fcarer lead trained to identify and
OL,10,Fsupport young carers. Given what these
OL,11,Fyoung people do for society, that's
OL,12,Fthe least we can do for them."
OL,14,FThe charity said it had released the
OL,15,Fsurvey findings a month into the
OL,16,Fschool year to highlight previous
OL,17,Fresearch showing that young carers
OL,18,Fmiss around a month of school each
OL,19,Fyear on average, compared with 13 days
OL,20,Ffor a child without a caring
OL,21,Fresponsibility.
